Package: dbConnection
Type: Package
Title: dbConnection
Version: 0.3.0
Author: David P.S. Fong
Maintainer: David P.S. Fong <vkelim@bigpond.com>
Description: R6 'object-oriented' objects for generic connection to databases. Preferentially uses 'pool' package, but does not depend on 'pool'.  Falls back to 'DBI' connections either if 'pool' is not available, or specifically if 'usepool == FALSE'. Exports (makes available) a single R6 object definition, 'dbConnection'.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
ByteCompile: true
Imports: 
 DBI,
 stringi,
 RSQLite,
 pipeR,
 glue
Suggests: 
 pool
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
